  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/8mug3Sv-jjo?si=c1cpOFN5MG2RRRUI\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Administrators when first accessing their project on <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0041be; text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;\" target=\"_blank\">Customer Portal</a> are presented with the activation form for their Liferay PaaS product. If this step was skipped, please navigate to </span><strong>Product Activation</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> on the left sidebar navigation and select </span><strong>Liferay PaaS.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Under </span><strong>Activation Status</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> you will see a link to complete your activation form only if the status is </span><strong>Not Activated. </strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Please click the link and fill out the required information:&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Project ID (Note: This Project ID cannot be changed.)&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Primary Data Center Region</span></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Liferay PaaS System Admin’s Email Address</span></li>\n\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For each System Admin contact</span>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">System Admin’s First Name</span></li>\n\t\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">System Admin’s Last Name&nbsp;</span></li>\n\t\t<li aria-level=\"1\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">System Admin’s Github Username</span></li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Critical Incident Contacts</span>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">select at least one incident contact from your current team members list</span></li>\n\t\t<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">more details:&nbsp;</span><a class=\"article-list-link\" href=\"/w/how-do-i-manage-my-incident-contacts\">How do I Manage my Incident Contacts?</a></li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To submit the form, you will have to provide at least 1 System Admin contact information.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once the form is submitted, your information will be sent to our Liferay team for processing and the Activation Status will change to </span><strong>In Progress.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Activation will be completed within 1-3 business days and Administrators will be notified via email. Your Activation Status will then change to </span><strong>Activated.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>please refer to <a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/liferay-cloud/getting-started/initial-setup-overview\">Liferay PaaS initial steps</a> to understand what is expected and steps to follow after the activation is done by Liferay</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HDM0599XV6CX8QJ7XF1KDBPR\">Developer Keys</h2>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you would like to download a developer key, please navigate to: <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/how-do-i-download-a-developer-key-How-do-I-download-a-Developer-Key\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">How do I download a developer key?&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
      },
